<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_311" id="154v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_311_r1l5"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> <expan>Ercʒbıſch<ex>of</ex></expan> ʒu Meincʒ etc </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_311_r1l6"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> als vns eẅr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>t</expan> hat von Strölın </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_311_r1l8">eẅr <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>Jud<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_311_r1l7">bey vns </ab></add> etc das haben wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Vnd als </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_311_r1l9">wır <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu eren . von eẅers vıcʒtums bett <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_311_r1l10"><expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Strölın <expan>Jud<ex>en</ex></expan> hab bey vns dıe auf <expan>dıeſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> ʒeıt ın <expan>keine<ex>m</ex></expan> verpott </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_311_r1l11"><expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> geleyt bey vns geben <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> bıs auf ſand Mıchelſtag ſchıerıſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_311_r1l12">Alſo <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> wır <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> ʒu lıeb / <expan>derſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> Strölın <expan>Jud<ex>en</ex></expan> hab bey vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_311_r1l14">
<add>das geleyt<ab facs="#facs_311_r1l13">geben vnd </ab></add> <expan>erleng<ex>en</ex></expan> bıs auf ſand <expan>walp<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>en</ex></expan> tag ſchıerıſt ın <expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan> maſſ als vor </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_311_r1l15"><expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lıchen</expan> Denn wo wır <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>furſtenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> dıenſt vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_311_line_1594704379670_66">wolgefallen etc <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>ſab<ex>at</ex>o</expan> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> <expan>aſſu<ex>m</ex>p<ex>ci</ex><hi rend="sup">o<ex>n</ex>ıs</hi></expan> marıe <expan>vırg<ex>in</ex>ıs</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_311" id="154v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>, <expan>erczbisch<ex>of</ex></expan> zu
                        Meincz etc.</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als uns ewr
                            <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>t</expan> hat
                        von Strölin ewr <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>jud<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<add>bey uns</add> etc., das haben wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>.
                        Und als wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> zu eren von ewers vicztums bett
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> des
                            <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Strölin
                            <expan>jud<ex>en</ex></expan> hab bey uns, die auf
                                <expan>dies<ex>elb</ex></expan> zeit in
                            <expan>keine<ex>m</ex></expan> verpott <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan>,
                        geleyt bey uns geben <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> bis <app>
<note><q type="date">auf sand Michelstag schierist</q>29.09.1421</note>
</app>, also <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> zu lieb
                            <expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan> Strölin <expan>jud<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        hab bey uns <add>das geleyt geben und</add>
<expan>erleng<ex>en</ex></expan> bis <app>
<note><q type="date">auf sand <expan>Walp<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>en</ex></expan>
                                    tag schierist</q>01.05.1422</note>
</app> in <expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan> mass als vor
                            <expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lichen</expan>. Denn wo wir
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>furstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> dienst und wolgefallen etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sab<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>assu<ex>m</ex>p<ex>ci</ex><hi rend="sup">o<ex>n</ex>is</hi></expan>
                        Marie <expan>virg<ex>in</ex>is</expan>.</ab>
</div>
